Masu masaukin baki sun gamsu da barin Rangers su fara wasa, da sanin cewa za su iya wahalar da 'yan wasa sababbi kan rashin nasara.
Kuma wannan ita ce hanyar da za a cimma manufa mai mahimmanci.
Rangers sun ba da kyauta kuma Livingston ya sami dama, Declan Gallagher da Robinson sun haɗu don taimakawa Menga, wanda ya sami damar shiga kuma ya zira kwallaye daga tsakiyar filin.
