Ba kasafai ake samun matsanancin yanayi a Arizona ba, amma hakan na iya faruwa a farkon mako mai zuwa saboda sauran tasirin da guguwar Rosa ta yi a cikin hamadar kudu maso yamma, yana haifar da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta ba da gargadin ambaliyar ruwa a ranar Litinin da Talata ga yankunan yammacin Arizona zuwa kudancin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, gami da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas, da Salt Lake City.
Ana sa ran Rosa za ta wuce Phoenix a ranar Talata, za ta yi karo da ruwan sama a ranar Litinin da daddare.
