Rosa, har yanzu tana cikin karfin guguwa a safiyar Lahadi da karfin iska mai karfin mil 85 a awa daya, mil 385 arewacin Punta Eugenia, Mexico kuma tana tafiya arewacin kasar da gudun mil 12 a awa daya.
Guguwar ta haɗu da yankunan ruwan sanyi a cikin Pacific kuma saboda haka ƙarfinta ya ragu.
Saboda haka, ana sa ran zai sauka a Mexico a matsayin guguwa mai karfin iska a ranar Litinin da yamma ko kuma da dare.
Ana iya samun ruwan sama mai yawa a wasu sassan Mexico, yana haifar da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa
Kimanin inci 3 zuwa 6 na ruwan sama ana tsammanin zai mamaye yankin Baja California zuwa yankin kudu maso yammacin Sonora, mai yiwuwa ya kai inci 10, weather.com ta ruwaito.
Daga nan Rosa za ta ratsa arewacin Mexico a matsayin guguwar da ta kai iyakar Arizona da safiyar Talata a matsayin matsin lamba, wanda zai ratsa Arizona da kudu maso Utah da tsakar dare a ranar Talata.
Babban hadarin da guguwar Rosa ko sauran ta iya haifarwa shine ruwan sama mai yawa a Baja California, yankin arewa maso yammacin Sonora, da yankin kudu maso yammacin Amurka  Cibiyar Guguwa ta Kasa (NHC) ta ce.
