Tun da China ta fi aiki a fannin ilimin kere kere, Amurka ta kamata ta ninka kudaden da za ta kashe wajen gudanar da bincike a fannin, in ji mai saka jari kuma mai aiki da A2 Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan magana ta zo ne bayan bangarori daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka sun yi sanarwa game da AI, koda kuwa Amurka gabaɗaya ba ta da wata dabarar AI ta yau da kullun.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirinta a bara: tana da burin zama ta farko a cikin kirkire-kirkire na AI nan da shekarar 2030.
"Sanya kudaden bincike na AI sau biyu yana da kyau, saboda sauran kasashe suna neman zama nesa da Amurka, kuma muna neman ci gaba na gaba a AI", in ji Lee.
ninka kudaden zai ninka damar da za a samu babbar nasara ta AI a Amurka, Lee ya fada wa CNBC a wata hira a ranar Lahadi.
Lea, marubucin littafin nan AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley da New World Order" wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, ya wallafa a wannan watan, wanda ya riga ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kera kere-kere na kasar Sin, Face++.
