Shirye-shiryen taron jama'a na Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne taron farko na taron jama'a na Trump na taron jama'a biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, gami da tsayawa a wasu wurare masu ban sha'awa da suka hada da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Bayan tabbatar da cewa an dage zaben ne domin ya zabi wanda zai zama babban alkalin kotun kolin, Trump ya yi niyyar gina goyon baya a gare shi a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar watan Nuwamba saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a kan majalisar idan aka yi zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia a daren yau kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon sa ta yanar gizo?
An shirya taron jama'a na Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na yamma ET a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Kuna iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta yanar gizo ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye akan YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai tattauna batun sauraron shari'ar da ake yi a wannan makon ga wanda zai zama babban alkalin kotun kolin kasar, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya kara tsananin damuwa bayan zargin lalata da aka yi masa da kuma cewa za a jinkirta zaben majalisar dattijai har na mako guda yayin da FBI ke binciken sa.
Amma babban burin taron shi ne taimaka wa jam'iyyar Republican ta samu ci gaba a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, yakin neman zaben shugaban kasar Trump ya ce gangamin taron jama'a guda biyar a mako mai zuwa na nufin "karfafa gwiwa ga masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisa yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban kasa don haka zai yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke fuskantar lokacin kamfen", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya ƙi bayyana sunansa.
An shirya taron ne a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, ana sa ran taron na daren nan zai gabatar da magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma jan hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia karo na biyu cikin wata guda, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump ya yi kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar Sanatan West Virginia na Republican wanda ya ragu a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ne don kokarin inganta sakamakon zabensa", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Tawagar Amurka ta nuna karfin gwiwa wajen ci gaba da fatan samun nasara a karawar da za a yi a ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman uku na gefe daya, zaman hudu na ranar Asabar da yamma shine abin da ake buƙata a gasar Ryder.
Motsawa na motsi shine tsarin wasanni wanda shine sakamakon binciken da 'yan wasan suka yi imani da shi, kuma babu wanda ya fi wannan a cikin wannan gasar.
A ina suke ganin za su samu ci gaba?
"A baya, suna da maki shida a gaba kuma yanzu suna da maki hudu, don haka ina tsammanin muna ɗaukar wannan a matsayin ɗan ƙaramin ƙarfi", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake wucewa a ranar.
Babu shakka Turai na da fa'ida domin tana da maki hudu a raga da sauran wasanni 12.
Amma Team America, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin cewa suna da ɗan ƙarfi kuma suna da abubuwa da yawa da za su iya motsawa, ba tare da ban da rukunin Spieth da Justin Thomas waɗanda ke wasa tare duk rana kuma kowannensu yana alfahari da maki uku daga cikin huɗu ba.
Spieth ya yi wasa da kyar daga filin farko zuwa filin kore kuma ya jagoranci da misali.
Muryar murna ta kara da cewa a lokacin da ya zo, ya yi wani muhimmin bugun jini don yin wasan da ya yi da Thomas biyu da biyu.
Hannuwan da ya buga da suka ci su a lamba 15 an yi maraba da su da irin wannan ihu, ihu da ke gaya muku cewa ya tabbata Amurka ba ta rasa ba.
"Dole ne ku yi aiki tuƙuru kuma ku damu da wasanninku", in ji Spieth.
Duk waɗannan 'yan wasan sun tafi yanzu.
Akwai ramuka 18 da za a yi wa alama.
'Yan wasa guda daya da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, wadanda ba a iya jayayya da su ba a gasar Ryder.
Ƙungiya ta musamman amma mai ban sha'awa daga Turai shine hudu zuwa hudu kuma zasu iya yin ba tare da kuskure ba.
"Moliwood" ita ce kawai ma'aurata da ba su yi bogey ba a ranar Asabar da yamma, amma sun kuma guje wa bogey a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma da kuma baya tara a ranar Jumma'a.
Wannan tseren, da kuma yadda suke nuna makamashi yana gudana zuwa da kuma daga wannan taron da ke da damuwa wanda ya tabbatar da cewa su 'yan wasan da za a ci a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood da Molinari da zai kulle yiwuwar cin nasarar Turai a lokacin da rana ta faɗi a kan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau idan an sanya su duka a cikin rami daban-daban a lokaci guda.
Amma, ba a daɗe ba kafin a yi magana game da nasarar Turai.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun rage aikin Sergio Garcia, gwarzon dan wasan kwallon hudu na safe, lokacin da aka hada shi da Alex Noren.
Wani bogey da biyu biyu a gaban tara kamar su tono rami wanda babu wani ɗan wasan golf na Spain da Sweden zai iya hawa.
Ko da yake, a ranar Lahadi babu wanda zai iya taimaka maka ka fita daga rami.
Wasanni na hudu da na hudu suna da kyau a duba su sosai saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, shawarwarin da ba su bayar ba da kuma yadda dabarun zasu iya canzawa a cikin minti daya.
A wannan lokacin, Turai ta yi wasa sosai a matsayin ƙungiya kuma ta ci gaba sosai a ranar ƙarshe, amma zaman hudu ya nuna cewa ƙungiyar Amurka tana da ƙarfin hali don yin wasa duk da shakku da wasu ke yi, musamman a Amurka.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai za ta yi amfani da damar da ta samu a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan da ta tashi daga wasannin hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar inda ta yi nasara 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Wasu 'yan wasa biyu Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci gasar da suka ci Tiger Woods da ya yi fama da samun maki hudu a gasar Le Golf National.
Kungiyar Turai Thomas Bjorn, wacce ke neman rike kambun da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta doke Amurkawa da suka yi kuskure a wasan kwallon hudu da safe, inda ta ci wasan 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da ƙarin juriya a cikin hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba za su iya rage rashi ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk na bukatar maki takwas daga wasanni 12 a ranar Lahadi domin rike kofin.
Fleetwood ita ce ta farko da ta fara buga gasar Turai da ta ci maki hudu a jere, yayin da ita da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da "Molliwood" bayan wasan karshen mako, suka zama na biyu da suka ci maki hudu a wasansu hudu na farko a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan hudu, sun kasance masu karfi don doke Woods da ke jefawa da kuma dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau da fifiko 5 & 4.
Woods, wanda ya yi aiki a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya yi fice a wasu lokuta amma ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 a wasan hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, ya huta a wasan hudu na safe, sannan ya dawo don yin hulɗa da Henrik Stenson a cikin hudu kuma ya rasa 2 & 1 daga Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - na farko da na uku a duniya.
Turai ba ta kai ga wannan ba duk da cewa rana tana da kyau kuma iska tana shawagi a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Masu cin kofin duniya sau uku Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa ma'auni ga Amurkawa da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara mai ban sha'awa 2&1 akan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain a cikin hudu sannan suka sake dawowa don doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a cikin hudu bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup inda wata kungiya ta dawo daga rashin nasara ta hudu zuwa wasa guda, ko da yake a matsayin mai tsaron gida Furyk kawai yana buƙatar maki don riƙe kyautar.
Amma, bayan sun kasance na biyu mafi kyau a cikin kwanaki biyu, ranar Lahadi ta yi kama da za ta wuce su.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba zai yiwu ba ta yi watsi da makaman ta ba tare da amincewa ba
A ranar Asabar, ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya sanar da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya game da takunkumin da ke ci gaba da zurfafa rashin amincewarsu da Amurka kuma ba zai yiwu kasar ta zubar da makaman nukiliyarta ba a cikin irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na kungiyar cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "manyan matakai masu kyau" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makamai masu linzami, rushe wuraren gwajin nukiliya, da kuma yin alkawarin ba za ta bunkasa makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga amsar da ta dace daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba za a sami amincewa a cikin tsaron kasa ba kuma a irin wannan yanayi ba zai yiwu mu cire makamanmu ba da farko".
Yayin da Ri ya sake maimaita irin wannan korafin daga Koriya ta Arewa game da juriyar Washington ga tsarin "mataki-mataki" na kawar da nukiliya inda za a hukunta Koriya ta Arewa don ɗaukar matakai a hankali, ya ba da sanarwa mai mahimmanci cewa ba su ƙi gaba ɗaya kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya ba.
Ri na nufin wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka fitar a taron koli tsakanin jami'an shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa da aka fara yi a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "yantar da yankin Koriya daga makaman nukiliya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta so kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53 a hukumance, amma Amurka ta ce Pyongyang dole ne ta dakatar da makaman nukiliyarta da farko.
Washington ta kuma yi watsi da kiran da ake yi na sassauta takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan 'denuclearisation first' kuma ta kara matsin lamba ta hanyar sanya takunkumi wanda ke kai ga cimma burinta ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma ta yi watsi da 'bayanan karshen yaki,'" in ji Ri.
"Ganin cewa takunkumi zai iya sa mu durƙusa shine mafarkin mutanen da basu san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, irin wannan takunkumi na ci gaba da ƙara mana shakku".
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump da shugabannin Amurka suka gabatar a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan ba.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya nuna tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya kara da cewa: "Idan bangaren da ke da matsala a wannan batun na yaduwar nukiliya shi ne Koriya ta Kudu maimakon Amurka, yaduwar nukiliya a yankin Koriya ba za ta sami irin wannan matsalar ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya bambanta da na bara, lokacin da ya yi jawabi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin rokar Koriya ta Arewa a kan Amurka ba zai yiwu ba bayan da "Shugaba Iblis" Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin rokoki" a kan aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya, ya yaba wa Kim saboda karfin gwiwar da ya nuna wajen daukar matakin kwance dukiyar, amma har yanzu akwai babban aiki da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da sanya takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da iyakacin lokaci don wannan, "Idan wannan ya ɗauki shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar - ba matsala", in ji shi.
China da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bukaci hukunta Pyongyang kan matakin da ta dauka.
Sai dai, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka, Mike Pompeo, ya shaida wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Dole ne a ci gaba da aiwatar da takunkumin Kwamitin Tsaro ba tare da bata lokaci ba har sai mun tabbatar da cewa an kammala, karshe kuma an tabbatar da kisan nukiliya".
Kwamitin Tsaro ya kara tsaurara takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun 2006 a kokarin dakatar da kudaden da Pyongyang ke baiwa shirin nukiliyarta da makaman ta.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma tafiyarsa ta ƙarshe ba ta tafi da kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa a zahiri an samu ci gaba, sai dai Koriya ta Arewa a cikin sa'o'i kadan ta yi zargin cewa ya yi "da'awar kamala".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a wani taron da ta yi da Moon a wannan watan cewa za ta rushe makaman nukiliyarta da kuma wuraren da take amfani da su idan Amurka ta dauki "matakan da suka dace".
Ya ce Kim ya umarce shi da ya "yi aiki daidai da" burinsa na tabbatar da tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma matsawa zuwa daidaita dangantaka da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna yin darasi game da samun isasshen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara ya sa duk daliban aji daya a can su kara bacci, a kokarin da suke yi na yaki da al'adar maza a cikin ilmantarwa da ke bunkasa ta hanyar maganin kafeyin da ake kira 'mutane-mutane-mutane'.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗaliban manyan jami'o'i a duniya sau da yawa ba su san kome ba game da yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ya tsara wannan darasi, wanda ya yi imanin shi ne na farko a Amurka.
Ta samu wahayi zuwa ga fara wannan darasi bayan ta ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
'A ƙarshe wata yarinya ta zo wurina kuma ta ce: 'Me ya sa aka gaya mini yanzu, a shekarata ta ƙarshe?'
Yarinyar ta ce babu wanda ya taɓa gaya mata game da muhimmancin barci - abin mamaki ne a gare ni,' in ji ta ga The Telegraph.
An fara wannan karatun ne a wannan shekarar, inda ake bayyana wa dalibai muhimmancin yadda samun isasshen barci ke taimakawa wajen samun nasara a makaranta da kuma wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyarsu.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin tabin hankali a makarantar likitancin Harvard kuma darektan zartarwa na jami'ar kiwon lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan ta gano cewa dalibai suna fama da karancin barci a duk tsawon mako.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya ya ƙunshi ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani zaman, an nuna hotunan ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai ke danna kofi, labule, riguna, da littattafai don samun bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da fitilu, da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki, da kuma muhimmancin tsarin barci.
A wani ɓangaren kuma, an bayyana wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci zai iya sa su kamu da ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar makarantar, tare da gumakan hulɗa, sannan ya sa masu halarta suyi tunani game da al'adarsu ta yau da kullun.
'Mun san cewa wannan ba zai canja halin ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun tabbata cewa suna da hakkin su sani - kamar yadda kai ma kake da hakkin sanin yadda shan taba yake shafan lafiyarka,' in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adun alfahari da 'dare,' ya ce, ya ci gaba da cewa, fasahar zamani da matsin lamba a kan dalibai da ke nufin rashin barci matsala ce mai girma.
Ya ce, yin isashen barci, mai kyau, ya kamata ya zama 'makaminmu na sirri' wajen magance damuwa, gajiya, da kuma alhini - har ma da guje wa yin nauyi, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta shiga yanayin yunwa, yana sa mutum ya ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, wani ɗan shekara 19 daga California wanda ke nazarin ilimin sunadarai da ilimin kimiyyar lissafi wanda ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara wannan darasi, ya halarci ɗayan azuzuwansa a shekarar da ta gabata a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ta ce wannan darasi ya buɗe mata idanu kuma ya sa ta shirya darussa ga dukan jami'ar.
Mataki na gaba, yana fatan cewa duk daliban digiri na biyu za a umurce su su kammala irin wannan karatun kafin su shiga wata cibiyar gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da kafa ƙararrawa don lokacin bacci, da ƙararrawa don farkawa, kuma su san tasirin hasken shuɗi da allon lantarki da fitilun LED ke fitarwa, wanda zai iya motsa sautin circadian daga cikin layin sa kuma ya haifar da matsalar bacci.
