Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones Kit Harington ya soki mummunan mutum
Kit Harington ya shahara sosai saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na HBO Game of Thrones.
Amma wannan ɗan wasan, 31, ya musanta stereotype na jarumi mai jaruntaka, yana cewa irin wannan rawar a kan allon yana sa matasa maza sau da yawa suna jin cewa dole ne su kasance masu ƙarfi don girmamawa.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin 'wani abu ba daidai ba ne' kuma ya yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance mummunan batun namiji a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda ya yi aure kwanan nan ga abokin aikinsa a Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, kuma 31, ya ce yana jin 'ƙarfi' wajen tattauna batun.
'Ina jin kaina, mai karfi sosai, a yanzu - ina ne mu ke da laifi game da wannan namiji? 'in ji shi.
'Me muke koya wa maza sa'ad da suke girma game da matsalolin da muke gani yanzu?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama mai alhakin bayyanar mummunan namiji tare da halayensa na maza.
Ya ci gaba: 'Wane hali ne aka haifa kuma menene aka koya?
Mene ne ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma kan titi, da ke sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su kasance da wannan yanayin domin su zama maza?
Ina tsammanin wannan ita ce babbar tambayar da muke yi a wannan zamanin - ta yaya za mu canza shi?
Domin babu shakka akwai abin da bai dace da matasa ba.'
A cikin hirar ta kuma yarda cewa ba za ta taka rawa a cikin prequel ko sequel na Game of Thrones ba yayin da jerin za su ƙare a bazara mai zuwa, yana cewa ta 'ƙare da fagen fama da dawakai'.
Daga watan Nuwamba Kit za ta fito a fim din Sam Shepard na True West, wanda ke da labarin wani mai shirya fim da kuma dan uwansa, wanda ɗan fashi ne.
Actor din ya bayyana kwanan nan cewa ya dauki haduwa da matarsa Rose a matsayin mafi kyawun dalilin da zai sa ya fice daga Game of Thrones.
'Na sadu da matata a wannan wasan kwaikwayon, don haka na sami iyali na gaba, kuma daga nan ne rayuwata ta fara' in ji shi.
Rose ta buga Ygritte, ƙaunataccen Jon Snow na Kit, a cikin wannan jerin almara na Emmy.
Ma'aurata sun yi aure a watan Yuni na 2018 a gidan Leslie na iyali a Scotland.
HIV/Aids: Kasar Sin ta samu karin kashi 14 cikin 100 na sabbin masu cutar
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar kanjamau.
Ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a ƙasar.
Kimanin sabbin mutane 40,000 aka samu a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sabbin cututtukan suna yaduwa ta hanyar jima'i, suna nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a sassan kasar Sin sakamakon ƙarin jini da ke dauke da cutar.
Amma, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu kowa, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na ƙasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, kowace shekara adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru zuwa 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana nuna nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT.
Domin tsattsauran ra'ayi na ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka na cututtuka suna zuwa ne daga rashin isasshen kariya ta jima'i a cikin wannan dangantaka.
Tun a shekarar 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar kanjamau ga kowa a kasar a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
