"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin kasa, da 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya wannan rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihi", in ji jakadan The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman ga taron jama'a a wani taron raye-raye a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
