Amurka za ta iya amfani da sojan ruwanta a matsayin "kulle" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida
"Idan ya cancanta" Washington na iya neman taimakon sojin ruwa don hana makamashin Rasha isa kasuwannin, gami da Gabas ta Tsakiya, Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke ya bayyana, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ya ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi zargin cewa, shigar da Rasha cikin Syria - musamman, inda take aiki a gayyatar gwamnati - wata hujja ce ta gano sabuwar kasuwar makamashi.
"Na tabbata dalilin da yasa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shine suna son zama dillalan makamashi, kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, Kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma, in ji jami'in, akwai hanyoyi da kuma hanyoyin da za a hana hakan.
"Amurka tana da wannan damar, tare da Sojojin Ruwa, don tabbatar da bude hanyoyin ruwa, kuma, idan ya cancanta, don yin toshewa, don tabbatar da cewa makamashi ba zai iya shiga kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi a gaban masu halartar taron da Alliance for Consumer Energy, wata ƙungiya mai zaman kanta da ke kiran kanta "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta yadda Washington ta yi amfani da yarjejeniyar da Rasha da Iran, ya ga cewa a cikin tasiri, suna da kama.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki a Iran da Rasha kusan shine, amfani da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yana mai nuni da Rasha a matsayin ɗaya daga cikin "masana a wannan fannin" tare da tattalin arzikin da ke dogara da burbushin mai.
