Moscow ta sha nanata cewa aikin famfo mai daraja dala biliyan 11, wanda aka tsara don ninka karfin bututun mai na yanzu zuwa mita biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa tsananin adawa da Washington ke yi wa aikin kawai don dalilai na tattalin arziki ne kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Na tabbata muna da ra'ayi daya cewa ba za a yi amfani da makamashi a matsayin kayan aiki don matsa lamba ba kuma cewa masu amfani da su su zabi masu samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Alexander Novak bayan ganawa da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Wannan halin na Amurka ya jawo martani daga Jamus, wanda ya sake jaddada jajircewarsu ga aikin.
Kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI), ta bukaci Amurka da ta guji tsoma baki a manufofin makamashi na Tarayyar Turai da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
