"Na riƙe hannunsa lokacin da ya daina numfashi kuma har yanzu bai daina numfashi ba har sai da ya mutu, a ƙarshe na yarda cewa ba shi da nasara", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa Daley ya yi gasa a gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
"Abin da na sani shi ne, wannan shi ne abin da na yi mafarkinsa a rayuwata - yin iyo a gaban taron mutane a gasar Olympics, babu abin da ya fi wannan", in ji ta.
Wannan kuma ya ba da wahayi ga zaɓin waƙarsa na farko - Proud by Heather Small - wanda ya kasance tare da ita a shirye-shiryensa don gasar Olympics kuma har yanzu yana sa ta yi rawar jiki.
Desert Island Discs shiri ne na BBC Radio 4 wanda ake watsawa a ranakun Lahadi da karfe 11:15 na BST.
Mickelson ya sauya rawar da aka yi masa a gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan golf na Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi yayin da yake buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47, amma dole ne ya canza rawar don kauce wa nasarar da ba ta dace ba.
Mickelson, wanda ya buga wasan shekara biyu a karo na 12 a tarihi, ya kasance a hannun kyaftin Jim Furyk don wasan hudu da kuma rukuni na hudu a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon kasancewa a tsakiyar wasan, kamar yadda ya saba yi wa Amurka, wannan babban zakara sau biyar ya raba lokacinsa tsakanin zama mai ba da shawara da kuma yin wasan a cikin wannan zangon, yana fatan gyara abin da ya dame shi.
Ba a taɓa kasancewa mafi kyawun mai buga golf ba duk da cewa a lokacin da yake kan gaba a rayuwarsa, wannan mutum mai shekaru 48 bai dace da bin hanya mai tsauri ba a Le Golf National, wanda ke ba da horo mai tsawo da tsauri ga kowane harbi mara kyau.
Kuma a fagen sa, ba abin tsoro bane ga Mickelson, a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi, da zai fafata da zakaran gasar Open ta Ingila Francesco Molinari, wanda ya yi aiki tare da sabon shiga Tommy Fleetwood don lashe dukkan wasanninsu hudu a wannan makon.
Idan wannan ɗan wasan golf na Amurka, ya fara wasanni 12 a cikin wasa guda da maki huɗu, ya fara da farawa mai zafi, to wasan Mickelson zai zama mai mahimmanci.
Furyk ya nuna cewa ya amince da wannan mutumin, ba don yana da abubuwa da yawa da zai faɗa ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci matsayinsa sosai a yau, ya bugi baya kuma ya rungume ni, ya ce zai kasance a shirye don wasan gobe.
"Ta kasance da tabbaci sosai.
Shi Hall of Famer ne kuma ya ba da gudummawa sosai ga wannan ƙungiyar a baya, da kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ba zan iya tunanin shi wasa biyu ba.
Na yi tunanin wasu, amma wannan ita ce hanyar da za mu yi wasa kuma wannan ita ce hanyar da muke tsammanin za mu bi.
Yana son ya ji daɗin wani yanayi dabam, kamar yadda yawancin mutane suke yi".
Mickelson zai wuce Nick Faldo a kan yawan wasannin Ryder Cup da aka buga a ranar Lahadi.
Wannan zai iya nuna ƙarshen aikinsa a gasar Ryder Cup wanda ba zai taɓa daidaita da ƙimar da ya kafa ba.
Mickelson ya ci 18 da ya ci 20 da kuma ci bakwai, duk da cewa Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa ya kawo wasu abubuwa da ba za a iya faɗi ga ƙungiyar ba.
"Yana da ban dariya, yana da hankali, yana da ban dariya, yana son yin ba'a da mutane, kuma shi mutum ne mai kyau a cikin ɗakin wasan kwaikwayo", in ji shi.
"Ina tsammanin matasa 'yan wasa suna da kyau tare da shi, wannan makon ma, wanda ya kasance mai ban sha'awa sosai don kallo.
Ya ba da abubuwa da yawa, fiye da wasa kawai".
Kyaftin Turai Thomas Bjorn ya san cewa babban fa'ida zai iya ɓace nan ba da jimawa ba
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din Turai, ya koya daga kwarewa cewa wanda ya jagoranci sosai zuwa wasan karshe na Ryder Cup zai iya zama tafiya mai ban sha'awa.
Dane ya fara bugawa a wasan 1997 a Valderrama, tare da kyaftin din Seve Ballesteros yana da maki biyar a kan Amurkawa, amma ya taba kaiwa ga ƙarshen layi tare da hanci tare da mafi ƙanƙanta, ya lashe 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Kuna ci gaba da tunatar da kanku cewa mun sami babban ci gaba a Valderrama; mun sami babban ci gaba a Brookline, inda muka yi asara, da kuma a Valderrama, inda muka ci nasara, amma kawai", in ji Bjorn, yana ɗaukar hoto, bayan kallon Class of 2018, ya ci 5-3 duka a ranar Juma'a da jiya tare da ci 10-6 a Le Golf National.
Saboda haka, tarihi zai nuna min da kuma duk wanda ke cikin tawagar cewa wannan ba shi da iyaka.
Gobe za ku shiga cikin wasa mai ban sha'awa.
Ka fita ka yi abin da ya dace.
Ba a gama ba har sai kun sami maki a kan allon.
Muna da manufa, kuma wannan manufa ita ce lashe wannan kyautar, kuma wannan shine abin da muke mayar da hankali.
Na dade ina cewa, ina mai da hankali ne kan 'yan wasan 12 da ke wajenmu, amma kuma mun san abin da ke wajen sauran 'yan wasan - 'yan wasan da suka fi kyau a duniya".
Bjorn ya yi farin cikin ganin 'yan wasan suna wasa a kan wani filin golf mai wuya, ya daɗa: "Ba zan taɓa yin nasara a wannan ba.
Gobe wata tauraruwa ce daban.
Gobe, 'yan wasa za su ci gaba, kuma wannan abu ne daban da za a yi.
Yana da kyau a fita waje tare da abokin aiki idan komai ya tafi daidai, amma idan ka fita waje kana wasa da kanka, to za a gwada cikakken iyawarka a matsayin ɗan wasan golf.
Wannan shi ne sakon da ya kamata ka gaya wa dukkan 'yan wasan, ka fitar da mafi kyawunka don wasan gobe.
Yanzu, ka bar abokin aikinka kuma dole ne ya tafi don ya kawo mafi kyawunsa".
Ba kamar Bjorn ba, abokin hamayyarsa Jim Furyk zai nemi 'yan wasansa su yi wasa da kyau fiye da yadda suke yi a matsayin yapasangann, sai dai ga Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka ci uku daga cikin maki hudu.
Furyk da kansa ya kasance a bangarorin biyu na wasan karshe na babban wasan, ya kasance wani ɓangare na ƙungiyar da ta ci nasara a Brookline kafin ta ƙare a shan kashi yayin da Turai ta yi "Miracle a Madina".
"Na tuna da kowace kalma", in ji shi a lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda Ben Crenshaw, shugaban 'yan wasan a 1999, ya tara 'yan wasansa a ranar ƙarshe.
"Muna da manyan wasanni 12 gobe, amma kuna son farawa da sauri kamar yadda kuka gani a Brookline, kamar yadda kuka gani a Madina.
Idan aka samu saurin gudu a hanya guda, hakan zai sanya matsin lamba a tsakiyar wasan.
Mun kuma tsara jerin sunayen 'yan wasa kuma mun sanya mutane a hanyoyi daban-daban da muke jin, ku sani, muna ƙoƙarin yin mu'ujiza gobe".
An ba Thomas aikin ƙoƙarin jagorantar tsayayya da Rory McIlroy a cikin wasan farko, tare da Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood, da Ian Poulter, sauran 'yan wasan Turai suna kan gaba.
"Na tafi tare da wannan rukuni na mutane a cikin wannan tsari saboda ina tsammanin zan iya rufe duk hanyoyi", in ji Bjorn game da zaɓin da ya yi.
An sake dakatar da sabon jirgin yakin Jamus
An ce sabuwar jirgin ruwan sojin ruwan Jamus zai fara aiki a shekarar 2014 domin maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba za a samu jirgin ba har sai shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin tsarin aiki da kuma karin kudin da ake kashewa, in ji kafafen yada labarai na kasar.
An dakatar da aikin "Rheinland-Pfalz", babban jirgi na sabon jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit da ke ambaton kakakin soja.
An yi alkawarin cewa za ta shiga cikin rundunar sojin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da suka biyo bayan bayarwa sun kawo cikas ga wannan babban shiri.
An ba da umarnin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg guda huɗu a cikin 2007 don maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Jirgin zai kasance sanye da manyan bindigogi, da jerin makamai masu linzami masu saukar ungulu, da makamai masu linzami masu saukar ungulu, da wasu fasahohin da ba a sani ba, kamar su radar, infrared, da kuma makullin sauti.
Sauran muhimman fasalulluka sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa - ya kamata ya yiwu a yi amfani da sabon jirgin ruwa na tsawon shekaru biyu daga tashar tashar jiragen ruwa.
Amma, wannan jinkiri na ci gaba da faruwa yana nufin cewa waɗannan manyan jiragen ruwa - da aka ce suna ba Jamus damar nuna ikonta a ƙasashen waje - za su zama tsofaffi da zarar sun fara aiki, in ji Die Zeit.
Wani jirgin ruwa mai dauke da makamai mai saukar ungulu mai suna F125 ya zama sanarwa a bara, lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta ki amincewa da shi kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa tashar jirgin ruwa ta Blohm & Voss da ke Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ruwa ta mayar da jirgin zuwa ga masu kera shi bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka mayar da jirgin ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu "kurakurai na software da na'urori" da suka sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka yi amfani da shi don aikin yaki.
Kuskuren software yana da mahimmanci saboda jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg za su yi aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120 - kawai rabin ma'aikatan da ke cikin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An kuma san cewa nauyin jirgin yana da yawa wanda zai rage aikinsa kuma ya iyakance ikon Navy don ƙara haɓaka a nan gaba.
An yi imani cewa wannan jirgin ruwan mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin jirage iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ban da lalacewar kayan aiki, farashin samar da dukan aikin - har da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin - ma matsala ce.
An ce ya tashi da ban mamaki zuwa €3.1 biliyan ($3.6 biliyan) - sama da farkon €2.2 biliyan.
Matsalar da ke tattare da wannan sabon jirgin ya zama mai mahimmanci saboda gargaɗin kwanan nan game da raguwar ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa sun "wuce jirgi da zai iya yin amfani da shi".
Jami'in ya ce matsalar ta daɗa muni da shigewar lokaci, domin tsofaffin jiragen sun daina aiki amma ba a samu waɗanda za su maye gurbinsu ba.
Ya yi nadamar cewa babu wani jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da zai iya shiga cikin Navy.
Ƙungiyar National Trust ta saurari rayuwar asiri na bat
Wani sabon bincike da aka yi a wani gona a ƙasar Scotland yana nufin ya gano yadda waɗannan tsuntsayen suke amfani da shimfidar wurare don neman abinci.
Ana sa ran cewa wannan binciken zai ba da sabon haske game da halayen waɗannan dabbobi masu tashi da ke tashi kuma zai taimaka wajen tsara ayyukan kiyayewa a nan gaba.
Masana kimiyya a National Trust for Scotland sun yi nazarin irin waɗannan dabbobi kamar su pipistrelle da sopran da kuma daubenton da kuma long-eared brown bat a gonar Inverewe a Wester Ross.
Za a saka na'urori masu ɗauke da bayanai a wurare dabam-dabam da ke kewaye da gidan don lura da ayyukan bat a duk lokacin.
Ma'aikatan NHS da masu sa kai za su kuma gudanar da binciken wayar hannu ta amfani da na'urar gano abubuwa.
Masanin sauti da ke nazarin dukan waɗannan bayanan zai san yawan kiran da ake yi da kuma irin nau'in da ake kira.
Sannan za a samar da taswirai da rahotannin mazauni don samar da hotuna masu girman shimfidar wuri da ke bayyana yadda suke.
Rob Dewar, mai ba da shawara kan kiyaye muhalli a NTS, yana fatan wannan sakamakon zai bayyana wuraren da ke da muhimmanci ga bat da kuma yadda kowane nau'in ke amfani da su.
Wannan bayanin zai taimaka wajen sanin amfanin da ake samu daga aikin kula da mazauni kamar samar da ciyayi da kuma yadda za a kiyaye gandun daji don bat da sauran nau'o'in da suka danganci.
Yawan 'yan damisa a Scotland da kuma sauran ƙasashen Ingila ya ragu sosai a cikin ƙarni da suka shige.
Wannan dabbar tana fuskantar barazanar gina gidaje da kuma lalata mazauninta.
Ƙari ga haka, iska da kuma hasken wuta suna kawo haɗari, kamar su takarda mai ruɓaɓɓen da ake sakawa don kama bat da kuma maganin da ake yi wa kayan gini da kuma hare-haren da ke faruwa a gidajen dabbobi.
Baƙar fata ba makafi ba ne.
Amma, domin yana farauta da dare, kunnuwansa sun fi idanunsa amfani wajen kama dabbobi.
Suna amfani da fasahar gano sautin sauti don gano kwari daidai da abubuwan da ke hana su tashi.
