Ronaldo wanda ya musanta zargin fyade yana shirya lauyoyi don su kai karar wata mujallar Jamus
Cristiano Ronaldo ya kira zargin fyade da ake yi masa "labaran karya ne", kuma ya ce mutane "suna son tallata kansu" ta amfani da sunansa.
Lauyanta zai kai karar jaridar Der Spiegel ta Jamus, wadda ta wallafa zargin.
An zargi dan wasan gaba na Portugal da Juventus da yiwa wata Ba'amurkiya, Kathryn Mayorga, fyade a dakin otal din Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
Daga bisani an yi zargin cewa ya biya ta da dala 375,000 don ta yi shiru game da lamarin, Der Spiegel ta ruwaito a ranar Jumma'a.
Da yake magana a wani bidiyo na Instagram Live ga mabiyansa miliyan 142 sa'o'i kadan bayan da aka bayar da rahoton, Ronaldo, mai shekaru 33, ya la'anci rahoton a matsayin "labaran karya".
"A'a, a'a, a'a, a'a, wannan ba haka ba ne.
Abin da suka fada a yau labaran karya ne", in ji wannan mai lashe Ballon d'Or sau biyar a gaban kyamarar.
"Suna son su tallata kansu ta amfani da sunana.
Hakan ya saba.
Suna son su zama sanannu ta wajen ambaton sunana, amma hakan wani ɓangare ne na aikin.
Ni mutum ne mai farin ciki kuma komai yana da kyau", in ji ɗan wasan yana murmushi.
Lauyoyin Ronaldo na shirin kai karar Der Spiegel kan zargin, wanda suka kira "ra'ayoyin da ke nuna rashin amincewa a fagen sirri", a cewar Reuters.
Lauyansa Christian Schertz ya ce zai nemi diyya a matsayin "da'awar rashin mutunci a cikin adadin da ya dace da tsananin cin zarafin, wanda zai iya zama ɗaya daga cikin manyan cin zarafin sirri a cikin 'yan shekarun nan".
An ce lamarin ya faru ne a watan Yuni na shekarar 2009 a wani dakin dakuna a Palms Hotel da Casino a Las Vegas.
Bayan sun hadu a wani gidan rawa, Ronaldo da Mayorga sun koma dakin dan wasan, inda ake zargin ya yi mata fyade, a cewar rahoton da aka shigar a Kotun Daular Clark da ke Nevada.
Mayorga ya ce Ronaldo ya durƙusa bayan abin da ya faru kuma ya gaya masa cewa "kashi 99 cikin dari" shi "mutum ne mai kyau" wanda ya ɓata rai kawai "kashi ɗaya cikin dari".
Takardun sun ce Ronaldo ya yarda cewa su biyu sun yi jima'i, amma bisa ga sha'awar juna.
Mayorga ya kuma ce ya je ofishin 'yan sanda kuma ya yi gwajin raunukansa a asibiti, amma daga baya ya amince ya warware batun a waje da kotu saboda yana jin "tsoron samun fansa" kuma yana tsoron "za a kunyata shi a fili".
Matar mai shekara 34 ta ce yanzu tana neman soke yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya saboda ta ci gaba da fama da rauni game da abin da aka zarge ta.
Ronaldo ya kusa komawa Real Madrid daga Manchester United lokacin da aka zargi harin, kuma a wannan bazarar ya koma babbar kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Italiya Juve a yarjejeniyar €100m.
