Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun auku a ƙasar Indonesia
Wata babbar girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu, a kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'ar da ta gabata, ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 384, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Rashin sadarwa ya sa jami'an bayar da agaji suka sami matsala wajen samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala, wani yanki da ke arewacin birnin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar da ta yi ƙarfin awo 7.5.
A Palu, bayan bala'in, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da birnin Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke kan iyakar wani kunkuru a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin yawan mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da haihuwa.
Donggala, a halin yanzu, gundumar da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) daga gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Wannan gundumar, wacce ita ce yankin gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardin, an kiyasta cewa tana da mazauna 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Babban cibiyar tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Kudu shine kifi da kuma noman shuka, musamman a gabar Donggala.
Duk da haka, kasancewar hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana taka muhimmiyar rawa a lardin, kodayake yawancinsa suna cikin Morowali, a gabar tekun Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa, bisa ga bayanan Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, mutane fiye da 200 sun mutu a tsunami kuma ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala sun rushe.
A shekara ta 1996, mutane tara sun mutu a tsunami a yammacin Donggala.
A cikin girgizar kasa, Indonesia tana cikin Ringin Wuta na Pacific kuma saboda haka girgizar ƙasa za ta faru a kai a kai.
Wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya-bayan nan su ne:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta auku a Indonesia, a bakin tekun yammacin lardin Aceh, a arewacin Sumatra, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami a ƙasashe 14, wanda ya halaka mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, kuma fiye da rabin waɗanda suka mutu a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta afka wa yammacin Sumatra.
A tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra, an yi asarar rayuka da yawa.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami a gabar teku ta kudu da ta kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afka wa tsibirin Mentawai, a gabar tekun Sumatra, kuma hakan ya haddasa tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Gundumar Pidie Jaya, Aceh, ta sha wahala daga girgizar kasa da ta haifar da lalacewa, tare da firgita daga mutanen da ke tunawa da lalacewar girgizar kasa da tsunami mai kisa a shekarar 2004.
Ko da yake ba a sami wata guguwar tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon rushewar ginin.
A shekarar 2018: Lombok, wanda ake kira tsibirin yawon bude ido, ya sha wahala daga wata babbar girgizar kasa da ta kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta lalata dubban masu yawon bude ido.
An Kama Ɗan Sara Palin na Biyu a Kan Tashin Hankali a Cikin Iyali
Track Palin, babban dan Sarah Palin, tsohuwar gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, an kama shi da laifin hari.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin mata, hana rahotanni na cin zarafin mata da kuma tsayayya da yunkurin kama shi, kamar yadda 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka sanar a ranar Asabar.
Bisa ga rahoton 'yan sanda, sa'ad da wata mace da ta san ta ke ƙoƙarin ta kira 'yan sanda don ta ba da rahoton wani laifi, sai ta ƙwace wayar daga hannun ta.
An mika Palin zuwa gidan yarin Mat-Su, inda aka ci tarar $500 ba tare da an bayar da belin ba, kamar yadda KTUU ta ruwaito.
Kamar yadda wata kafa ta yada labarai ta ruwaito, Palin ta halarci shari'ar ranar Asabar, inda ta bayyana cewa "ba ta da laifi, ta tabbata" lokacin da aka tambaye ta game da kare kanta.
Palin tana fuskantar manyan laifuka uku na Class A, wanda zai iya sanya ta a gidan yari har shekara guda da kuma tara dala 250,000.
Bugu da ƙari, an kuma tuhume shi da laifin aikata laifi na Class B, wanda ya kai hukuncin ɗaurin rana ɗaya da kuma tara $2,000.
Ga Palin, wannan ba shine karo na farko da ake tuhumar ta ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge shi da kai hari kan mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarta, Sarah Palin, ita ce ta tuntubi 'yan sanda don yin rahoto game da zargin da ake yi.
Yanzu haka an kai karar ne zuwa kotun tsaron Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an gurfanar da shi a gaban kotu kan aikata laifukan tashin hankali a cikin gida, hana bayar da rahoton aikata laifukan tashin hankali a cikin gida, da kuma mallakar bindiga a cikin maye, wanda kuma ya shafi lamarin.
Abokinsa ya zarge shi da ya buge fuskarsa.
A shekara ta 2016, Sarah Palin ta fuskanci zargi daga ƙungiyar tsoffin sojoji saboda ta danganta tashin hankalin ɗanta da PTSD sakamakon aikinsa a Iraki.
