Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi a yankewa wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci hukuncin kisa a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York, inda mutane takwas suka mutu - hukuncin da ba a taba yi ba a jihar dangane da aikata laifuka na tarayya tun 1953.
Ana zargin Saipov, mai shekara 30, da aikata wani mummunan aiki ta hanyar buga motar haya daga Home Depot a kan masu tafiya da kekuna a kan hanyar keke a kan West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su ba da hujja cewa Saipov "da gangan" ya kashe mutane takwas kuma "da gangan" ya haifar da mummunan rauni, bisa ga wata sanarwa ta son yanke hukuncin kisa, wanda aka gabatar a gundumar kudu ta New York.
Bisa ga takardun kotu, waɗannan tuhume-tuhume biyu za su iya kai ga hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun lauyoyi ta gurfanar da Saipov a kan wasu laifuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai a cikin aiwatar da barazanar, wanda yawanci ake amfani da shi a gaban masu gabatar da kara a cikin laifukan da suka shafi aikata laifuka, da kuma laifuka na tashin hankali da kuma kokarin lalata motar.
A cewar mai gabatar da kara, harin ya bukaci "tsarin da ya dace da kuma kyakkyawan shiri", kamar yadda ya nuna laifin Saipov da aka aikata da "mummunan, mummunan, da kuma mummunan hali".
An bayyana a cikin wasiƙar da ta ce, "Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, haɗari, da asarar ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco. 
Wadanda suka mutu biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma kenan da Kudancin New York ya yanke hukuncin kisa.
A watan Satumbar 2009, an yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa da kisan wasu masu sayar da magunguna biyu.
An yi kisa a kotun tarayya ta New York a shekarar 1953, a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa a kan yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg da matarsa da kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Bisa ga takardun kotu, Saipov, daga Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
Sa'ad da masu bincike suka tambaye shi, ya ce yana farin ciki da abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya kuma bayyana wa hukumomi cewa harin da ya kai ya samo asali ne daga bidiyon ISIS da ya kalli ta wayar sa, kamar yadda ake zargin.
Ya kuma nemi a saka tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22 da ake yi masa.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "a fili ya yi takaici" da hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"A ra'ayinmu, yanke shawarar kashe shi maimakon karbar hukuncin kisa na rai ba tare da kariya ba zai kara wa mutanen da ke cikin lamarin rauni", in ji Patton.
A baya bayan nan, masu kare Saipov sun roki mai gabatar da kara da kada a yanke masa hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisa sun ce Nigel Farage ne ke da alhakin tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi kira ga 'yan adawa da su yi zanga-zanga a taron 'yan Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su 'ji zafi' na masu adawa da Tarayyar Turai - saboda wani dan majalisa, Theresa May, ya ba da shawarar shiga cikin tattaunawar da EU.
Wani mai goyon bayan jam'iyyar Conservative, Peter Bone, ya shaida wa wani zanga-zanga a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya "ya kamata ta fice" a yanzu idan Farage ya zama sakataren Brexit.
