Bone ya yi watsi da shawarar cewa ra'ayin jama'a na iya haifar da canji tun lokacin da aka kada kuri'ar a 2016: "Gaskiyar cewa tunanin mutanen Burtaniya ya canza kuma suna son yanayin ya kasance, ba gaskiya bane".
