Wannan harbi na farko na cinikayyar kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China yana da ban tsoro, kuma yayin da yakin ya yi nisa da kawo karshen, rashin jituwa tsakanin kasashen biyu na iya zama mai amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, a cewar masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, ya fara gargadin kasar a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da ake fitarwa daga kasar Sin ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminum.
An fara saka karin kudade masu muhimmanci a wannan makon da sabbin kudade da suka shafi kayayyaki masu darajar dala biliyan 200 (£150bn), wanda hakan ya sanya haraji kan rabin dukkan kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka ta kasar Sin.
