China ta nemi ta yi daidai da Amurka daya-daya, kuma tattalin arzikinta na biyu mafi girma a duniya ba zai canza ba nan ba da jimawa ba.
Faɗa wa Washington ta yi watsi da ita yana nufin ta bi son zuciyarta, amma faɗawa Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban China.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta iya taka wasanninta daidai, matsin lamba na cinikin Amurka na iya taimaka wa China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro tsakanin tattalin arzikin biyu.
